WEBVTT

00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:54.479
You...

00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:55.799
Why are you still here?

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:57.960
I can't bear to leave this place.

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:00.359
Is that so?

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:03.039
The will states...

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:05.480
that I inherit this house now.

00:01:06.599 --> 00:01:07.239
And I also...

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:08.959
don't plan to stay in Tai Cheng for long.

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:11.560
So I plan to spend a few days...

00:01:12.239 --> 00:01:13.560
clearing these things out,

00:01:14.879 --> 00:01:15.879
and then selling the house.

00:01:18.359 --> 00:01:20.879
If you have an attachment to this house,

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:23.280
I'll recommend you to the new buyer,

00:01:23.719 --> 00:01:25.719
so you can continue as the housekeeper here.

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:34.519
Where do you think the money is?

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.159
The person closest to Zhao Qishan...

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:45.799
was his wife, Di Fu.

00:01:46.359 --> 00:01:48.200
And Di Fu left all his inheritance...

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.040
to her younger sister.

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:54.599
I get it.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:57.280
That damn witch.

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:58.799
She wanted to get back at all of us.

00:01:58.799 --> 00:01:59.599
Even in death,

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:00.719
she wants to take revenge on us.

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:03.879
Li Ran definitely knows something.

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:09.280
The story she told earlier...

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:11.680
I don't believe a word of it.

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:14.120
Even though everyone is making up stories,

00:02:14.599 --> 00:02:15.240
and she's no exception.

00:02:16.599 --> 00:02:18.199
But she specifically emphasized...

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:20.080
that she hadn't contacted Di Fu in years.

00:02:20.280 --> 00:02:22.879
That was too deliberate.

00:02:23.039 --> 00:02:24.960
Li Ran got over three million.

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:25.759
Plus the property.

00:02:30.759 --> 00:02:31.840
The money is in the house.

00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:37.159
Are you leaving Tai Cheng?

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:38.199
Yes.

00:02:39.319 --> 00:02:40.400
Does that cop know?

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:45.360
What do you mean?

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:50.039
If the police don't know,

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:52.960
that saves me a lot of trouble.

00:03:00.599 --> 00:03:01.639
We'll split up.

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.319
You go find Li Ran.

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:04.960
I'll go to the Tower of Babel.

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:06.159
Okay.

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:13.879
When you find her...

00:03:14.759 --> 00:03:15.400
what should I do?

00:03:18.360 --> 00:03:19.360
The usual way.

00:03:20.159 --> 00:03:21.240
Make it clean.

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:23.120
Don't leave any traces.

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:25.039
Talk! Where is the money?

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:46.879
It's here.

00:03:47.719 --> 00:03:49.000
You can't escape.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.439
Here is the DNA test you asked for,

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:53.479
Detective Qi.

00:03:53.599 --> 00:03:54.759
As per your instructions,

00:03:55.039 --> 00:03:56.960
I've sent a few guys to the hotel to find Li Ran.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:58.520
It says the probability...

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:00.039
is less than 0.04%.

00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:01.879
That body isn't Lin Niannian.

00:04:03.199 --> 00:04:04.879
Several cars just left the compound.

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:06.000
They're heading towards the villa...

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.080
and the hotel.

00:04:10.479 --> 00:04:11.560
They're all going after Li Ran.

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:12.159
Let's go to the villa.

00:04:12.479 --> 00:04:12.840
Okay.

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:22.079
Miss Li.

00:04:37.519 --> 00:04:38.319
Miss Li!

00:04:48.959 --> 00:04:49.680
They aren't here yet.

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:50.480
Let's go inside first.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:26.600
Li Ran!

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:29.160
Li Ran!

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:32.839
She's still alive.

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:34.240
Call an ambulance!

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.040
Follow me.

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:06.480
Where is that little girl?

00:06:06.839 --> 00:06:07.480
Who are you?

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:08.360
Police! Don't move!

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:20.439
You guys hold this position.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:30.279
Li Ran!

00:06:42.759 --> 00:06:43.240
Li Ran!

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:07.560
What is this place?

00:07:09.319 --> 00:07:10.560
You were looking for this door.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:31.959
Auntie

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:32.720
Sit down.

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:39.279
Hello, your coffee.

00:07:39.639 --> 00:07:40.439
Thank you.

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.680
I know what you want to ask.

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:47.319
To be honest,

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:49.720
this is the topic our family least wants to mention.

00:07:49.879 --> 00:07:50.920
You mean...

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.879
Li Ran's past.

00:07:55.519 --> 00:07:56.279
You know the password.

00:07:58.720 --> 00:07:59.560
I don't know.

00:08:00.399 --> 00:08:01.480
These two paintings are the mechanism.

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:02.439
How did you know?

00:08:02.439 --> 00:08:03.120
Detective Qi,

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:04.839
my mind is a mess right now.

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:06.720
At a time like this,

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:07.720
are you still not telling the truth?

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:10.360
I'm sorry.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:11.920
Your hand is injured.

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.120
I once received a letter from my sister.

00:08:24.519 --> 00:08:25.879
She told me to come to the Tower of Babel

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:27.079
to find a secret room.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:29.439
She said

00:08:30.319 --> 00:08:32.159
her most important things are inside.

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:38.519
This is my sister's dying wish,

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.080
and also my privacy.

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.559
That's why I didn't say anything.

00:08:48.159 --> 00:08:49.440
Let's bandage your hand first.

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:55.679
Turn Botticelli's painting

00:08:55.679 --> 00:08:57.480
of Dante's Inferno around.

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:02.080
How similar it is to the Tower of Babel.

00:09:03.879 --> 00:09:05.200
The very bottom of this painting

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:06.320
was originally the bottom of hell.

00:09:07.320 --> 00:09:08.360
After turning it upside down,

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:12.159
it actually becomes the heaven everyone yearns for.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.039
By the same logic,

00:09:16.799 --> 00:09:18.080
if you take the Tower of Babel longing for heaven

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.279
and rotate it upside down,

00:09:20.679 --> 00:09:21.919
heaven becomes hell.

00:09:23.879 --> 00:09:24.360
Miss Li,

00:09:24.919 --> 00:09:26.039
you really are clever.

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:29.480
How did you figure out they were the mechanism?

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:33.120
Botticelli's masterpiece,

00:09:33.759 --> 00:09:34.480
Dante's Inferno,

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:37.960
is the Western world's depiction of hell.

00:09:38.879 --> 00:09:40.080
Could it be that these two paintings

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:41.960
have some connection?

00:09:42.559 --> 00:09:43.639
Come with me to the dining room

00:09:43.879 --> 00:09:44.399
to eat something.

00:09:44.919 --> 00:09:45.440
The Tower of Babel

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:48.039
was created by the painter Bruegel

00:09:48.519 --> 00:09:49.840
in 1563,

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:52.240
based on a story

00:09:52.600 --> 00:09:53.120
from the Bible.

00:09:53.799 --> 00:09:56.120
Perhaps humans wanted to use this tower

00:09:56.840 --> 00:09:57.879
to reach straight to heaven.

00:09:58.840 --> 00:10:00.159
Because the name of this villa

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:01.600
is the Tower of Babel.

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.519
Alright, go to sleep.

00:10:15.519 --> 00:10:16.320
I guessed.

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:20.600
I just felt those two paintings looked similar,

00:10:21.639 --> 00:10:22.720
and suddenly thought

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:23.919
I could try that out.

00:10:27.759 --> 00:10:28.399
However,

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:30.000
finding this secret room

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:31.919
was purely accidental.

00:10:44.919 --> 00:10:46.799
It seems we've really fallen into hell this time.

00:10:48.879 --> 00:10:49.720
Then let's finish

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:51.480
the story we haven't finished telling,

00:10:53.039 --> 00:10:54.799
and solve the unsolved puzzles.